WEBVTT

00:01.912 --> 00:03.444
Russ: <i>My work is in the ghetto.</i>

00:03.464 --> 00:05.367
Lina: <i>I don't have an office.</i>

00:05.387 --> 00:06.546
Russ: <i>My commute is longer.</i>

00:06.566 --> 00:07.674
Lina: You get paid more.

00:07.694 --> 00:10.319
Well, I have to manage employees.

00:10.321 --> 00:12.404
Lina: I have to manage second-graders.

00:12.406 --> 00:14.874
I don't understand.
Why are we having this fight again?

00:14.894 --> 00:17.950
Because you still won't admit
that my job is worse than yours.

00:17.970 --> 00:20.690
- Because I... (crashing)
- Shh.

00:21.658 --> 00:23.246
What was that?

00:24.450 --> 00:26.984
I don't know.
It sounded like it came from the backyard.

00:27.004 --> 00:28.253
(dog barks)

00:30.013 --> 00:31.724
This is exactly the home invasion

00:31.726 --> 00:33.592
we always talked about
needing to be prepared for

00:33.594 --> 00:34.843
and we never did.

00:34.845 --> 00:36.345
You're gonna get killed.

00:36.347 --> 00:37.763
I'm gonna get raped and killed.

00:37.765 --> 00:39.264
Don't be so sure about the order.

00:39.266 --> 00:41.084
Can you see anything?

00:41.456 --> 00:43.402
Russ: No.

00:44.158 --> 00:45.604
I'm sure it's probably fine.

00:45.606 --> 00:46.855
Lina, come on. (gasps)

00:46.857 --> 00:48.440
(screams)

00:48.837 --> 00:51.517
There's a man in the backyard.

00:52.727 --> 00:55.135
S02E06
Murder!

00:55.259 --> 00:57.542
sync and corrected by ninh
www.addic7ed.com

